{"tid":2329389,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年涉藏汽油彈 警員自言能分辨普通市民與非法集結人士 「唔會三五成群唔會著黑衫」","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:10:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"22a19a8b76b6da215f09b8af69885e22b346b306","tid":2329389,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:08:45.000Z","msg":"去年11月網民連日發起全城大三罷運動，其間三名青年涉因藏有汽油彈及雷射筆被拘控，案件今續審。辯方盤問截停被告的警員時指出，警員不能分辨普通市民與參與非法集結的人，更指被告當時根本沒逃跑，只是站著；警員不同意，強調：「街外人喺馬路行，唔會三五成群，唔會著黑衫；好明顯普通人就普通人，非法集結就非法集結。」<br />\n<br />\n負責截停及為本案次被告搜身的警員李寶成（譯音）供稱，他發現包括次被告在內的三、四名黑衣人逃跑，於是追前，不足10秒後追上次被告並將他按在地上，從次被告身上搜出雷射筆、波鞋、泳鏡等物，搜身過程由同袍拍下。<br />\n<br />\n從警方影片可見，當李從次被告背囊搜出波鞋時，<strong>李問次被告波鞋用途，次被告答「練跑」。其後李又搜出兩支水及一支寶礦力，李讓次被告各喝一口。當李再從次被告身上搜出泳鏡，李反問次被告謂：「又游水？又跑步？」</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/SWM4WRNBKFCTFLSSHMVBLDSWKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FSWM4WRNBKFCTFLSSHMVBLDSWKI%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28TX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=57100f50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FSWM4WRNBKFCTFLSSHMVBLDSWKI%2F&h=e8ed7019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/SWM4WRNBKFCTFLSSHMVBLDSWKI/</a>"},{"pid":"bd3beed9c017a5a29eafb81f8f5f910dd49ba670","tid":2329389,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fde16bca863cdffd5ee6a364de2fe57f341d11","tid":2329389,"uid":65888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:10:11.000Z","msg":"未玩過triathlon?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950dc1767a85bf720ae4360df10465bf5429d69b","tid":2329389,"uid":